ed"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"2 garlic cloves"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"400 g tinned chopped tomatoes (1 x 400 g tin)"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"2 tsp ground cumin"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"½ tsp garam masala"}],"nutrition":["per 1 portion","1137 kJ \/ 272 kcal","24.9 g","9.5 g","14.9 g"],"hintsAndTricks":["Steam rice in the simmering basket while the fish is baking in the oven. There is no need to wash the mixing bowl as any residual sauce will only enhance the flavour of the rice.","This deliciously aromatic dish produces mouth-wateringly flaky fish. It is a welcome variation from the heavier, highly spiced curry dishes and, served with rice it can be a complete meal."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h","4 portions"]}